z''(t)+Az'(t)+B=0
u''(t)+u'(t)+1=0
u(t)=z\left(\frac{t}{A}\right) + \left(\frac{B}{A^2}-1\right)t
 u = \frac{A^2}{B} z 
 x = A t 
 z'' = B u'' 
 z' = \frac{B}{A} u' 
 z''(t) + Az'(t) + B = 0 
 u''(x) + u'(x) + 1 = 0. 
 u = \frac{A^2}{B} z 
 du = \frac{A^2}{B} dz 
 x = A t 
 dx = A dt 
 z'=\frac{dz}{dt} = \frac{\frac{B}{A^2} du}{\frac{1}{A} dt} = \frac{B}{A} \frac{du}{dx}
 z''= \frac{d}{dt}(\frac{dz}{dt}) = A \frac{d}{dx}(\frac{B}{A}\frac{du}{dx})=B\frac{d^2u}{dx^2}
 B\frac{d^2u}{dx^2} +B\frac{du}{dx}+B=0 
 u''(x) + u'(x) + 1 = 0. 
