z\left(t\right)=w\left(\xi\right)
w
 \frac{\mathrm{d}z}{\mathrm{d}t}=\frac{\mathrm{d}w}{\mathrm{d}\xi}\frac{\mathrm{d}\xi}{\mathrm{d}t}=w'\xi_t\\ \frac{\mathrm{d}^2z}{\mathrm{d}t^2}=w''\xi_t^2+w'\xi_{tt} 
\left(w''\xi_t^2+w'\xi_{tt}\right)+\left(Aw'\xi_t\right)+B=0
\xi_t^2
w''+\left(\frac{\xi_{tt}}{\xi_t^2}+\frac{A}{\xi_t}\right)w'+\frac{B}{\xi_t^2}=0.
